'''Hiong-gong haak-gaa-faa''' heh [[Hiông-kóng|Hiong-gong]] [[Sîn-kie|Sin-geh]] yin-gi-min [[si thaai min-hai]] zi yit geh Haak-gaa-ngin si-yung. Yin-wui Hiong-gong geh Haak-gaa-ngin du zaap zung hiong Sin-geh, yu ho-yi haam zu '''Sin-geh Haak-gaa-faa'''. Cang wui Hiong-gong dai ngi thaai hon-yi hai fong-ngien. Hiong-gong haak-gaa-faa fun-phu zi Gong, Giu, Sin-geh gok khi. Thet-phit zaap-zung yi saan-fung khaau doh geh Sin-geh dung, yi Sin-geh dung gang yit thu heh Haak-gaa zung-sim-khi geh zu saang phu-fan. Cit-sip nen-theui fui-ci haau doh Haak-gaa-ngin maau gong zi-gaa geh faa. Zin yung Gong-fu-faa/Hiong-gong Yit-yi.


